e Flesh and the Devil – reappear in different contexts: the world of immigration, of white women desiring Muslim men, and the present-day "freedom fighters."  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 0aEnglish fictiony20th centuryxHistory and criticism. 0aMuslims in literature. 0aOrientalism in literature. 0aTravelers' writings, Englishy19th centuryxHistory and criticism. 0aTravelers' writings, Englishy20th centuryxHistory and criticism. 4aHistorische Berichte. 4aOrientalismus. 4aReiseberichte. 4aSarazenen. 7aHISTORY / Medieval.2bisacsh  aHistorical Narratives.  aOrientalism.  aSaracens.  aTravel Narratives.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2022 Part 1z978311076682008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021 Englishz978311075400108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021z9783110753776oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural, Area Studies 2021 Englishz978311075412408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural, Area Studies 2021z9783110753899oZDB-23-DKU0 cEPUBz97815015131070 cprintz978150151791440uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978150151336740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781501513367423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781501513367/original  a978-3-11-075400-1  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021 Englishb2021  a978-3-11-075412-4  EBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural, Area Studies 2021 Englishb2021  a978-3-11-076682-0  DG Plus DeG Package 2022 Part 1b2022  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LT  aEBA_ECL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  